## 🛠 Development

### Running the Application

```bash
# Start the web interface (default port 5000)
python3 run_cli.py gui

# Run with debug mode enabled
python3 run_cli.py gui --debug

# Run on a different port
python3 run_cli.py gui --port 8080
```

### Stopping the Application

Press `Ctrl+C` in the terminal where the app is running.

If you need to kill it from another terminal:
```bash
# Kill process on port 5000 (macOS/Linux)
lsof -ti :5000 | xargs kill -9
```

### Restart Shortcut (macOS/Linux)

```bash
# Kill existing process and restart in one command
lsof -ti :5000 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null; python3 run_cli.py gui
```

